    "Sis Ricke’y": {
      "created": "2026-04-04T19:00:39.372Z",
      "entries": [
        {
          "id": 1775329239372,
          "seq": 1,
          "text": "During a time of difficulty, though I had my church family here in the US, TWC Ministries was also my family. I would go online to their prayer meeting and Bible study and just reason with them and pray with them and it would lighten my spirit nights upon nights. I’m thankful for their presence and their vision, I’m happy for every area of growth that the Lord has given them and I’m so blessed to be apart of a body that doesn’t even know what my face looked like but found it fit in a time of deep despair and mourning to be a place of encouragement. The people here are always excited to pray and to study the Word and is authentic about their love for God. It is amazing how great of a work God is doing here and I pray for future times to just meet those who I have spoken to and been with online. They’ve loved me and tenderly cared for my soul as necessary. Big up to TWC Ministries",
          "date": "4/4/2026",
          "time": "3:00:39 PM",
          "iso": "2026-04-04T19:00:39.185Z"
        }
      ]
    }
